Immigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectCanada-British Columbia Immigration Agreement ** Amendment **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration, to enter into an agreement to replace the Express Entry Schedule 2015 of the Agreement with the Express Entry Schedule 2018, which includes new data elements and disclosure provisions related to the administration of British Columbia's Express Entry provincial nominee program.
